  4,11,"Nyankopֽ»n retu mofo fa mo mma ho: ֶ†barima (baako) ky־µfa (wֽ» awugyade־µ mu) tes־µ mmaa mmienu ky־µfa. S־µ mmaa no boro mmienu a, wֽ»n ky־µfa y־µ nky־µmu mmi־µnsa mu mmienu wֽ» de־µ (owufoֽ» no awu) agya no mu. Nas־µ ֽ»baa no y־µ baako p־µ a, ־µne־µ ֽ»benya (emu) fa. S־µ (owufoֽ» no) wֽ» ba a, nג€™awofoֽ» no mu biara ky־µfa wֽ» de־µ (owufoֽ» no awu agya no mu) y־µ nky־µmu nsia mu baako. Nas־µ onni ba ־µna nג€™awofoֽ» na ־µredi nג€™ade־µ a, ־µne־µ ֽ»maame ky־µfa y־µ nky־µmu mmi־µnsa mu baako. S־µ (owufoֽ») no wֽ» nuanom a, ־µne־µ ֽ»maame ky־µfa y־µ nky־µmu nsia mu baako, wֽ» akyire yi a yayi nsamanse־µ a ֽ»yֽ»e־µ afiri mu, anaas־µ yatua ־µka biara awie. Moawofoֽ» ne mo mma, monnim nea neho mfasoֽ» b־µn mo paa. (Woi y־µ) ahy־µde־µ a efiri Nyankopֽ»n hֽ». Nokor־µ s־µ Nyankopֽ»n ne Onimdefoֽ», ֶ†ne Onyansafoֽ»"
  4,12,"De־µ moyerenom bewu agya no nso, s־µ wֽ»ג€™nni ba a, ־µfa y־µ modea; nas־µ wֽ»n wֽ» ba nso a, ־µne־µ moky־µfa y־µ de־µ wֽ»n awu agya no mu nky־µmu nnan mu baako, wֽ» akyire yi a yג€™ayi nsamanse־µ a ֽ»yֽ»e־µ, anaas־µ (yג€™atua) ־µka (biara) awie. De־µ monso (mobewu) gya no s־µ monni ba a, wֽ»n ky־µfa a ־µwֽ» mu y־µ nky־µmu nnan mu baako; nas־µ mowֽ» ba nso a wֽ»n ky־µfa wֽ» de־µ moagya no mu y־µ nky־µmu nwֽ»twe mu baako, wֽ» akyire yi a yג€™ayi nsamanse־µ afiri mu anaas־µ yג€™atua ־µka biara awie. S־µ ֽ»barima anaa ֽ»baa a yֹ›redi nג€™adeֹ› no nni agya anaa ֽ»ba, na s־µ ֽ»wֽ» nua-barima anaas־µ nua-baa a (wcn yj nna mma a), ־µne־µ ( cbarima baako no anaa cbaa baako no) ky־µfa y־µ nky־µmuu nsia mu baako; na s־µ wֽ»n dodoֽ» boro saa a, ־µne־µ wֽ»ג€™mֽ»mu nky־µ nky־µmu mmi־µnsa mu baako, wֽ» akyire yi a yayi nsamanse־µ afiri mu, anaas־µ yatua ־µka biara awie, aber־µ a monnha obi. Woi y־µ ahy־µde־µ a efiri Nyankopֽ»n hֽ». Onyankopֽ»n ne Onimdefoֽ», ֶ†ne Ntoboase־µ Hene"
  4,13,"(De־µ yaka akyer־µ mo yi) y־µ Nyankopֽ»n mmra. Obi a ֽ»b־µy־µ sotie ama Nyankopֽ»n ne Nesomafoֽ» no, ֶ†de no b־µkֽ» Soro Aheman a nsubֽ»nten nenam ase־µ no mu, emu na ֽ»b־µtena, na ־µno ne nkonimdie k־µse־µ paa no"
  4,14,"Obi nso a ֽ»b־µy־µ Nyankopֽ»n ne Nesomafoֽ» as־µm ho asoֽ»den, na ֽ»b־µto Nyankopֽ»n mmra no, ֶ†de no b־µkֽ» Amane-hunu gyem, ־µhֽ» na ֽ»b־µtena afe bֽ»ֽ», na ֽ»benya animguase־µ asotwee"